      "description": "<div><p>From pick up at your Cruise ship, Hotel, or Athens residence sit back in the comfort of one of our new Luxury Class Mercedes Vehicles as your experienced informative professional tour driver takes you on a private tour of all the Athens Highlights including the Acropolis, New Acropolis Museum, Arch of Hadrian, Temple of Zeus, Olympic Stadium, Parliament &amp; Traditional National Guards, and National Archaeological Museum, so you won't miss anything during your visit.\nOur Flexible Booking Options allow you to include a wonderful Traditional Lunch (Silver Option), Expert guiding with a Licensed Professional Guide who will be with you for 3 hours to cover the Acropolis and Acropolis Museum (Gold Option), or both Lunch plus Guide (Platinum Option), whilst a Family &amp; discount option is also available, as well as a Half-Day option including an expert guide for those preferring a shorter tour.\nPlease note that for bookings of 8 or more persons, a private guide is automatically included.</p></div>",
